Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - User per case, aggregated by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to the duration of Completed + In Call within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - User in variants leading to Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait - User and the subsequent Completed + Resolved when Completed + In Call does not occur
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User in cases that include Completed + In Call versus cases that do not
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - User grouped by resource
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities are present
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - User in high-frequency variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time it takes Accepted + Wait - User to be followed by Accepted + In Progress in variants that eventually reach Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total waiting time to Accepted + Wait - User after the first occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in cases ending with Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait - User in variants where Completed + In Call appears before resolution, compared to variants where it appears after
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Elapsed time between the start of a case and Accepted + Wait - User in processes that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that loop back to Accepted + In Progress after Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs
